aom.scripting.xs.rm

Class ObjectDef

  • Object
    • ObjectDef

  • public class ObjectDef
extends Object

    This class provides a collection of RM commands concerning Object Definitions.

    Object Definitions are used to place objects on the map.

    Author
    Mythic_Freak - mythic.freak[a]gmail.com
